{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1152431, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 227872, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还能报销？问问医院工作人员", "timestamp": 1614401848, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152465, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 227872, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "需要转诊单      去三院看病的时候留着那些票据什么的   如果一张票据写不下的那种要去门诊楼一楼打详细的单子", "timestamp": 1614402239, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152481, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 227872, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1.去校医院对应科室开转诊单，并在一楼导诊台处盖章\n2.在三院就医后留存黄色有盖章的收据和处方（有时候一张收据打印不下所有明细，需要去门诊自助机打印收据明细）\n3.就医完成后拿这转诊单和就医留存下来的收据去校医院报销\n如果已经在北医三院看完了，可以去校医院补转诊单（急诊不用补，其他的需要）；另外一张转诊单可以多次就医，但最好保证在一个月之内", "timestamp": 1614402454, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152489, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 227872, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不是所有就医都可以报销，参见公费医疗范围（校医院不报销的去北医三院看一样不给报，应该是美容相关的都不给报销）", "timestamp": 1614402540, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152492, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227872, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "给Carol点赞", "timestamp": 1614402575, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152551, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 227872, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 开完转诊单之后就可以直接去三院挂号看病嘛？转诊单在看病的时候有用嘛？\n", "timestamp": 1614403634, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152569, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227872, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 转诊单只是报销用的，和你去三院看病没关系，看病时没用", "timestamp": 1614404022, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152573, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227872, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 去三院看病就正常挂号正常看，只不过看完病要开收据而已", "timestamp": 1614404056, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1153441, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 227872, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "啊！谢谢BOBCAROLDAVE！！", "timestamp": 1614414480, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1154080, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 227872, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Alice……", "timestamp": 1614420544, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 17, "pid": 227872, "reply": 10, "tag": null, "text": "请问在北医三院就医后回校医院报销是怎样个流程呀？直接去三院就好么，回来需要带啥东西做什么操作啥的，是看啥病都能报销么？", "timestamp": 1614401613, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1614420545, "url": "", "vote": {}}}